Beatty, Appellant, v. Theleinann, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 5, 1890.) Plaintiff appeals from an order entered May 15, 1890, declaring action abated. *952J. M. Williams, for appellant. Fallon, Brunnemer & Crandall, for respondent.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs. See 8 N. Y. Supp. 645.
